OL,3,CWhat is Hezbollah and how is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Iran war?
OL,6,FIsrael has intensified its attacks on
OL,7,FHezbollah in Lebanon in recent days,
OL,8,Fwith the latest strikes killing at
OL,9,Fleast 182 people in Beirut, against
OL,10,Fthe backdrop of a two-week ceasefire
OL,11,Fagreed upon between Iran, the US and
OL,12,FIsrael.
OL,14,FHezbollah leader Naim Kassem is among
OL,15,Fthose killed, according to an Israeli
OL,16,FDefence Forces statement posted on X
OL,17,Fon Thursday, as Israel insists that
OL,18,Fthe militant group is not a part of
OL,19,Fthe ceasefire arrangement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
