OL,3,CWhat is Hezbollah and how is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Iran war?
OL,6,FITV News explains what Hezbollah is
OL,7,Fand how the group is involved in the
OL,8,Fcurrent conflict in Iran.
OL,10,FWhat is Hezbollah?
OL,12,FHezbollah is a Shia militant and
OL,13,Fpolitical force based in Lebanon that
OL,14,Fhas been designated a terrorist group
OL,15,Fby many Western countries, including
OL,16,Fthe UK.
OL,18,FIt was founded in 1982 after the
OL,19,FLebanon War, which saw Israel occupy
OL,20,Fmuch of the south of Lebanon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
