OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775769064
OL,3,CWhat is Hezbollah and how is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Iran war?
OL,6,FThe group specifically set out to copy
OL,7,Fthe model of Ayatollah Khomeini's
OL,8,FIranian Revolution in 1979 and has
OL,9,Fbeen an anti-Israel, anti-western
OL,10,Forganisation ever since.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FIt has since also become a powerful
OL,18,Fforce in the region with a large
OL,19,Fmilitary, which some say outnumbers
OL,20,FLebanon's own national army.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
