OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775769064
OL,3,CWhat is Hezbollah and how is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Iran war?
OL,6,FNumerically, Hezbollah is the largest
OL,7,Fnon-state military organisation on the
OL,8,Fplanet.
OL,10,FHezbollah has also become a legitimate
OL,11,Fpart of Lebanese politics, leading to
OL,12,Faccusations that it is a state within
OL,13,Fa state.
OL,15,FThe group currently holds 15 seats in
OL,16,Fthe parliament and is part of the
OL,17,Fseven-party caretaker government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
