OL,3,CWhat is Hezbollah and how is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Iran war?
OL,6,FThe country is now bitterly divided
OL,7,Fbetween Hezbollah, its allies and
OL,8,Fopponents ` paralysing the political
OL,9,Fsystem.
OL,11,FHezbollah's rise to power in Lebanon
OL,12,Fhas weakened the country's standing
OL,13,Fwith international partners.
OL,15,FIran is a key ally of Hezbollah, and
OL,16,Fthe Gulf states, who are largely anti-
OL,17,FTehran, have backed away from the
OL,18,Fgroup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
