OL,3,CWhat is Hezbollah and how is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Iran war?
OL,6,FIsrael continued to build up its
OL,7,Ffirepower around the north of its
OL,8,Fborder and the Israeli military moved
OL,9,Finto southern Lebanon.
OL,11,FIsrael and Hezbollah have exchanged
OL,12,Ffire in the weeks since then, with
OL,13,FNetanyahu saying the IDF would
OL,14,F"continue to strike Hezbollah wherever
OL,15,Fnecessary, until we restore full
OL,16,Fsecurity to the residents of the
OL,17,Fnorth".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
