OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775769064
OL,3,CWhat is Hezbollah and how is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Iran war?
OL,6,FOn April 1, Iran's new supreme leader
OL,7,FMojtaba Khamenei, appointed after his
OL,8,Ffather Ali Khamenei was killed by US
OL,9,Fforces, sent a letter to Hezbollah
OL,10,Fleader Naim Qassem to pledge Iran's
OL,11,Fcontinued support for the group.
OL,13,FThe ranks of Hezbollah have been
OL,14,Fdiminished in recent years as Israel
OL,15,Fhas targeted and eliminated many of
OL,16,Fits top officials, including leader
OL,17,FHassan Nasrallah.
OL,19,FDoes the current ceasefire apply to
OL,20,FHezbollah?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
