PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775769064
OL,3,CWhat is Hezbollah and how is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Iran war?
OL,6,FIsraeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,7,FNetanyahu said on Wednesday that the
OL,8,Fcurrent two-week ceasefire deal
OL,9,Fdoesn't cover fighting against
OL,10,FHezbollah in Lebanon.
OL,12,FIsrael's military said later that
OL,13,Ffighting and ground operations
OL,14,Fcontinue.
OL,16,FHowever, Farhan Haq, deputy
OL,17,Fspokesperson for the United Nations
OL,18,Fsecretary general, said a pause in
OL,19,Ffighting should be seen as a chance to
OL,20,Fbring peace between Israel and Lebanon
OL,21,Ftoo.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
