CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775769064
OL,3,CWhat is Hezbollah and how is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Iran war?
OL,6,F"The ceasefire between the US and Iran
OL,7,Foffers an opportunity to prevent
OL,8,Ffurther loss of lives between Lebanon
OL,9,Fand Israel," UN Deputy Spokesperson
OL,10,FFarhan Haq said in New York.
OL,12,F"Now is the time to pursue talks to
OL,13,Fresolve outstanding differences and
OL,14,Fwork towards a permanent ceasefire and
OL,15,Fa long-term solution to the conflict.
OL,16,FThere is no military solution to the
OL,17,Fconflict."
OL,19,FWhat is its relationship with Hamas?
