OL,3,CWhat is Hezbollah and how is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Iran war?
OL,6,FBoth Hezbollah and Hamas are backed by
OL,7,FIran, which provides both with
OL,8,Ftraining, funding and military
OL,9,Fequipment.
OL,11,FThe two groups have become closer in
OL,12,Frecent years, with many Hamas leaders
OL,13,Fnow living in Beirut.
OL,15,FAlthough they often support each other
OL,16,Fin their sparring with Israel, the two
OL,17,Fgroups do have differences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
