OL,3,CWhat is Hezbollah and how is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Iran war?
OL,6,FHezbollah is not a Palestinian
OL,7,Forganisation and is Shia Muslim,
OL,8,Fwhereas Hamas and the vast majority of
OL,9,FPalestinians are Sunni Muslims.
